data = data.dropna()

```python
high_prices=data['High'].values
low_prices=data['Low'].values
mid_prices=(high_prices + low_prices)/2
```


```python
mid_prices[1]
```

<pre>
1773.5
</pre>

```python
def normalization_Y (y): #변수 정규화
    y_std = y.std()
    y_mean = y.mean()
    y_norm = (y - y_mean) / y_std
    
    return y_std,y_mean,y_norm

def denorm(y,y_std,y_mean): #변수 역정규화
    return y * y_std + y_mean
```


```python
conf = {'gold':{'i':[],'MAE':[],'MSE':[],'RMSE':[],'R2' : []},'dollar':{'i':[],'MAE':[],'MSE':[],'RMSE':[],'R2' : []},'coin':{'i':[],'MAE':[],'MSE':[],'RMSE':[],'R2' : []}}
for i in range(1,151,1):
    seq_len=i # 최근 며칠을 보고 예측할지 정함
    sequence_length = seq_len+1

    result=[]
    for index in range(len(mid_prices)-sequence_length):
        result.append(mid_prices[index: index+sequence_length])
    
    result = np.array(result)

    row = int(round(result.shape[0]*0.7))
    row_1 = int(round(result.shape[0]*0.9))# 7:2:1 비율
    train = result[:row,:]
    val = result[row:row_1,:]
    test = result[row_1:,:]
    np.random.shuffle(train)
    np.random.shuffle(val)

    x_train=train[:,:-1]
    x_train = np.reshape(x_train,(x_train.shape[0],x_train.shape[1],1))
    y_train=train[:,-1]

    x_val=val[:,:-1]
    x_val = np.reshape(x_val,(x_val.shape[0],x_val.shape[1],1))
    y_val=val[:,-1]

    x_test=test[:,:-1]
    x_test = np.reshape(x_test,(x_test.shape[0],x_test.shape[1],1))
    y_test=test[:,-1]
    
    xtr_std,xtr_mean,x_train_norm = normalization_Y(x_train)
    xts_std,xts_mean,x_test_norm = normalization_Y(x_test)
    xv_std,xv_mean,x_val_norm = normalization_Y(x_val)

    ytr_std,ytr_mean,y_train_norm = normalization_Y(y_train)
    yts_std,yts_mean,y_test_norm = normalization_Y(y_test)
    yv_std,yv_mean,y_val_norm = normalization_Y(y_val)
    
    model = Sequential()

    model.add(LSTM(i,return_sequences=True,input_shape=(i,1)))

    model.add(LSTM(64,return_sequences=False))

    model.add(Dense(1,activation='linear')) # 다음날 1일의 결과예측

    model.compile(loss='mse',optimizer='adam')

    model.summary()
    
    model.fit(x_train_norm,y_train_norm,
         validation_data=(x_val_norm,y_val_norm),
         batch_size=32,
         epochs=10)
    g_pred = model.predict(x_test_norm)
    original_y_test = denorm(y_test_norm,yts_std,yts_mean)
    original_y_pred = denorm(g_pred,yts_std,yts_mean)

    mae = mean_absolute_error(original_y_test,original_y_pred)
    mse = mean_squared_error(original_y_test,original_y_pred)
    rmse = mse ** 0.5
    r2 = r2_score(original_y_test, original_y_pred)

    conf['gold']['i'].append(i)
    conf['gold']['MAE'].append(mae)
    conf['gold']['MSE'].append(mse)
    conf['gold']['RMSE'].append(rmse)
    conf['gold']['R2'].append(r2)
```
